"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-13-team-gb-star-demands-apology-mistake-cost-olympic-gold-medal-21415931\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GBshooter Amber Rutter has demanded an apology after a critical mistake saw her denied gold in the women's skeet at theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Team GBshooter Amber Rutter\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"an apology\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 51}, {\"ngram\": \"a critical mistake\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's skeet\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympics\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a tense final, a shoot-off was required in to separate Great Britain's Rutter and Chile's Francisca Crovetto after they tied on 55 shots from 60 targets.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.884403171194085, \"rank\": 0.07247788874496738, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8179175682134513, \"rank\": 0.11766463456408131, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\", \"score\": 0.9999995782860404, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Francisca Crovetto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tense final\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoot-off\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 173}, {\"ngram\": \"55 shots\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"60 targets\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair still could not be split after three shoot-off rounds but Rutter was then adjudged to have missed a shotwhich replays appeared to show she hit.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"three shoot-off rounds\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"Rutter\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"a shotwhich replays\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter contested the call but the judges did not overturn the decision and could not check on a video assistant system with the technology not in use at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rutter\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"the call\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 481}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"a video assistant system\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"the technology\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the controversial decision a week on from her final, the 26-year-old said she feels she is owed an apology by the sport's governing body and wants to speak out to help 'spark change'.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the controversial decision\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"an apology\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 744}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's governing body\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"spark change\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Due to a poor and incorrect decision by all three referees I was denied the opportunity to continue in the shoot off and chance at Olympic Gold,' Rutter, who gave birth to her first child just three months ago, said on Instagram.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.206977677872483e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a poor and incorrect decision\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"all three referees\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the shoot\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Gold\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"her first child\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'After the negativity I felt around catching Covid before Tokyo 2020 and the games becoming such a bad headspace for myself, I have said in many interviews I really did not want to get sucked into the negativity of what could've have been.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999605025169965, \"rank\": 3.949903706724658e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the negativity\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"such a bad headspace\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"many interviews\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the negativity\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'However, after being sat reading through so many of your comments with clear photographic evidence of me hitting the target.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your comments\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"clear photographic evidence\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1395}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I owe it not just myself but the entire shooting community to highlight and address the matter.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Every athlete, especially at the Games deserves to compete on a fair playing field.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every athlete\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair playing field\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether that be through experienced and exceptional judging, or new technologies such as VAR which we have always had in place previously at ISSF competitions.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6255906567665417e-22, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"experienced and exceptional judging\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"new technologies\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"ISSF competitions\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'At this point in time, I can not imagine a huge amount will be done, and that is not what I am looking for.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge amount\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, I do believe some accountability needs to be taken to acknowledge and an apology for the incorrect decision and furthermore a plan to prevent something like this happening in the future.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some accountability\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"the incorrect decision\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'There were multiple occasions through the final day where other shooters had a similar experience to myself and I am sure have the same feelings as myself.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple occasions\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the final day\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"other shooters\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar experience\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the same feelings\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope to use this platform I have right now to try and spark change in our sport.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this platform\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are at an elite level and these mistakes I believe should not even be a possibility.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an elite level\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"these mistakes\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope we can work together, athletes, coaches, officials to create something better.\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more stories\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport page\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Metro Sport\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest news onFacebook\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"TwitterandInstagram\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Convicted rapist Steven van de Velde sobs as he reveals he considered quitting Paris Olympics ArrowMORE:Olympic volunteer 'found next to girlfriend's corpse' hours after closing ceremony ArrowMORE:Australian breakdancing officials reveal reason why Raygun was selected for Olympics Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2656, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999986926829384, \"rank\": 1.3073188595762897e-06, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour